00:33:59,704 --> 00:34:02,915
They will continue the same
way they are going on now--

630
00:34:02,916 --> 00:34:05,418
through bribery, mostly--

631
00:34:05,418 --> 00:34:08,003
...but this will be
a chance for the people

632
00:34:08,004 --> 00:34:11,298
themselves to have a direct
say in the government.

633
00:34:11,299 --> 00:34:13,676
It costs so much now
to get elected

634
00:34:13,677 --> 00:34:15,804
that the congressmen
aren't any of them free.

635
00:34:15,804 --> 00:34:17,847
They belong to the people
who paid for their elections.

636
00:34:17,847 --> 00:34:19,390
They don't belong
to any of us at all.

637
00:34:19,391 --> 00:34:20,725
I mean, how many times

638
00:34:20,725 --> 00:34:22,852
have you heard someone
complaining about something

639
00:34:22,852 --> 00:34:24,979
but totally unable
to do anything about it?

640
00:34:24,980 --> 00:34:26,606
And besides that,

641
00:34:26,606 --> 00:34:28,774
it makes government
responsive to the people.

642
00:34:28,775 --> 00:34:29,901
You need an alternative route.

643
00:34:29,901 --> 00:34:31,694
If the congress is
bought out on an issue,

644
00:34:31,695 --> 00:34:33,655
like they are on nuclear power,
for example,

645
00:34:33,655 --> 00:34:35,448
